Motormaster decides to close his hand to muffle Squawktalks voice. He olds
open the other hand for Beastbox, who jumps up and transforms into his
hand. "And were off" yells Astroblast as he takes off closing the shuttle
hatch, soaring towards the Cybertronian Fire.
